Class Population

java.lang.Object
planet_earth.Population
Direct Known Subclasses:
Graphics
public class Population extends Object
The Population class is fundamental to analyze the data to be collected for each generation by establishing whether there is stability or not. Save through static attributes: - the parameters a , b , c - the number of four types per generation
